quran[37]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,Pus mein qasam khata hun sitaron kay girnay ki
  56,76,Aur agar tumhen ilm hoto yeh boht bari qasam hai
  56,77,Kay be-shak yeh quran boht bari izzat wala hai
  56,78,Jo aik mehfooz kitab mein darj hai
  56,79,Jissay sirf pak log hi chu saktay hain
  56,80,Yeh rabul aalameen ki taraf say utra hua hai
  56,81,Pus kiya tum aisa baat ko sirsari (aur mamooli) samajh rahe ho
  56,82,Aur apney hissay mein yehi letay ho kay jhutlatey phiro
  56,83,Pus jabkay rooh narkharay tak phonch jaye
  56,84,Aur tum uss waqt aankhon say dekhtay raho
  56,85,Hum uss shaks say banisbat tumharay boht ziyadah qareeb hotay hain lekin tum nahi dekh saktey
  56,86,Pus agar tum kissi kay zair-e-farman nahi
  56,87,Aur iss qol mein sachay hoto (zara) iss rooh ko to lotao
  56,88,Pus jo koi barah-e-elaahi say qareeb kiya hua hoga
  56,89,Ussay to rahat hai aur ghizayen hain aur aaram wali jannat hai
  56,90,Aur jo shaks dahanay walon mein say hai
  56,91,To bhi salamti hai teray liye kay tu dahanay walon mein say hai
  56,92,Lekin agar koi jhut lanay walon gumrahaon mein say hai
  56,93,To kholtay huye garum pani ki mehmaani hai
  56,94,Aur dozakh mein jana hai
  56,95,Yeh khabar sirasir haq aur qaton yaqeeni hai
  56,96,Pus tu apney azeem-ul-shaan perwerdigar ki tasbeeh ker
  57,1,Aasmanon aur zamin mein jo hai (Sub) Allah ki tasbeeh ker rahey hain woh zabardast ba-hikmat hai
  57,2,Aasmanon aur zamin ki badshahat ussi ki hai.woh hi zindagi deta hai aur mot bhi aur woh her cheez per qadir hai
  57,3,Wohi pehlay hai aur wohi peechay wohi zahir hai aur wohi makhfi aur woh her cheez ko bakhoobi janney wala hai
  57,4,Wohi hai jiss ney aasmanon aur zamin ko cheh (6) din mein peda kiya phir arsh per mustawi hogaya Woh (Khoob) jaanta hai uss cheez ko zamin mein jaye aur jo uss say niklay aur jo aasmanoon say neechay aaye. aur jo kuch Charh ker uss mein jaye aur jahan kahin tum ho woh tumharay sath hai aur jo tum kerahey ho Allah dekh raha hai
  57,5,Aasmanoon ki aur zamin ki baadshahi ussi ki hai aur tamam kaam ussi ki taraf lotaye jatay hain
  57,6,Wohi raat ko din mein lejata hai aur wohi din ko raat mein dakhil kerdeta hai aur seenoon kay bhedon ka woh poora aalim hai
  57,7,Allah per aur uss kay raool per eman ley aao aur uss maal mein say kharch kero jiss mein Allah ney tumhen doosron ka janasheen banaya hai pus jo tum mein say eman leyen aur kheraat keren unhen boht bara sawab milay ga
  57,8,Tum ALLAH per eman kiyon nahi latay ? Halankay khud rasool tumhen apney rab per eman lanay ki dawat dey raha hai agar tum momin ho to who to tum say mazboot ehad-o-paymaan bhi ley chukka hai
  57,9,Woh (ALLAH) hi hai jo apney banday per wazeh aayaten utaarta hai takay who tumhen andheron say noor ki taraf ley jaye yaqeenan ALLAH taalaa tum per narmi kernay wala reham kernay wala hai
  57,10,kertay' darasal aasmanon our zamin ke meeress ka malik (tanha) Allah hi hai tum main say jin logo ney fatah say pehlay fi subilillah diya hai our qitaal kiya hai woh (doosron kay) barabar nahi bulkay unn say boht baray darjay kay hain jinhon nay fatah kay baad kheyraaten den our jahad kiyey haan bhalaee ka wada to Allah taalaaka unn sab say hai jo kuch tum ker rahey ho uss say Allah khabardaarhai
  57,11,Kon hai jo Allah taalaa ko achi tarah qarz dey phir Allah Taalaa issay uss kay liye barhata chala jaye our uss kay liye pasandeedah ajar sabit hojaye
  57,12,(Qayamat Kay) din tu dekhay ga kay momin mardo our orton ka noor unn kay aagay aagay our unkay dayen dor raha hoga aaj tumhen inn jannaton ki khushkhabri hai jinkay neechay nehren jaari hain jin main humesha ki rehaeesh hai yeh hai bari kaamyabi
  57,13,Uss din munafiq mard-o-orat eman walon say kahan gay kay humara intizar to kero kay hum bhi tumharay noor say kuch roshni hasil kerlen jawab diya jayega kay tum apney peechay lot jao our roshni talash kero phir inkay our unkay darmiyan aik deewar haaeel kerdi jayegi jiss main darwaaza bhi hoga uss kay androoni hissay main to rehmathogi our bahir ki taraf azab hoga
  57,14,Yeh chilla chilla ker unn say kahen gey kay kiya hum tumharay sath na thay woh kahengay kay haan thay to sahi lekin tum ney apney app ko fitnay mein phansa rakha tha our intizar mein hi rahey our shak-o-shuba kertay raheyour tumhen tumhari fazool tamannao ney dhokay mein hi rakha yahan tak kay Allah ka hukum aa phoncha our tumhen Allah kay baray mein dhoka denay walay ney dhokay mein hi rakha
  57,15,Algharz aaj tum say na fidya (aur na badla) qabool kiya jayega our na kafiron say tum (sab) ka thikana dozakh hai wohi tumhari rafiq hai our woh bura thikana hai